      "text": "NOTE -- Always wrap the function which you are using in           \n                eventlistner,considering that function needs to be \n                improved later,  \n                Because         \n                to use .removeEventListener we need the exact same   \n                function that was used to add it( i.e not any other  \n                function that look same )\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NOTE -- Always wrap the function which you are using in            \n                eventlistner,considering that function needs to be \n                improved later,  \n                Because         \n                to use .removeEventListener we need the exact same   \n                function that was used to add it( i.e not any other  \n                function that look same )\n",
      "autoResize": false,
